  "analyst_note": "CVE-2021-22205: Unauthenticated RCE via ExifTool image upload parsing. Affects GitLab CE/EE 11.9+. Fixed in 13.10.3, 13.9.6, 13.8.8. The /api/v4/version endpoint is unauthenticated only on public instances or with a valid token. If 401 is returned, version cannot be determined — treat as inconclusive. Public exploits weaponize ExifTool DjVu file parsing.",
